        "timestamp": 1702240774
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>You could also have <code>Num.iterate : Num *, state, (state -&gt; state) -&gt; state</code> where e.g. <code>Num.iterate 2 x f</code> is <code>f (f x)</code></p>",
